i5.las2peer.p2p.pastry

Class PastGetContinuation<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • i5.las2peer.p2p.pastry.PastGetContinuation<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T -
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    rice.Continuation<rice.p2p.past.PastContent,java.lang.Exception>

    public class PastGetContinuation<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements rice.Continuation<rice.p2p.past.PastContent,java.lang.Exception>
    A Continuation for retrieving stored envelopes from the past p2p artifact storage. For usage, you can either do something else while waiting for the result of the past(ry) retrieval and check the Continuation's state via isFinished() or do a (non) blocking wait for the result via waitForResult() or getResultWaiting().
